Link = Shortcut : A coonection between File Name and Actual Data on Disk
command : ln : link name

Hard Link : Delete/Rename original file No affect to link
            file inode number Equal link inode number
            
Soft Link : Delete/Rename original file Affect to link
            file inode number Not equal link inode number


ln -s /path/ LinkName : Create soft link of a File

ls -li : check inode number

ln /path/ Linkname : create hard link of a file


